1082
00:50:55,892 --> 00:50:57,902
(Rushing down immediately)

1083
00:50:58,102 --> 00:51:00,232
I served them jeon.

1084
00:51:01,102 --> 00:51:03,101
Look who's all over the place again.

1085
00:51:03,102 --> 00:51:04,172
Get a grip.

1086
00:51:04,642 --> 00:51:05,871
I'll double-check.

1087
00:51:05,872 --> 00:51:06,902
(The Good Boy has become bad.)

1088
00:51:07,542 --> 00:51:09,672
