1089
00:51:09,972 --> 00:51:12,042
(Walking up two stairs at a time)

1090
00:51:12,412 --> 00:51:13,681
I'm so sorry.

1091
00:51:13,682 --> 00:51:17,011
- This is Korean meatballs.
- Okay, yes.

1092
00:51:17,012 --> 00:51:19,322
- I was confused. It's so busy.
- It's okay.

1093
00:51:19,852 --> 00:51:20,891
- Okay.
- All right.

1094
00:51:20,892 --> 00:51:22,721
