1098
00:51:28,762 --> 00:51:29,931
- Six.
- Six?

1099
00:51:29,932 --> 00:51:31,162
Table six.

1100
00:51:31,332 --> 00:51:32,432
Six.

1101
00:51:32,832 --> 00:51:34,372
It's for Table six, right?

1102
00:51:35,402 --> 00:51:36,402
- The beef tartare.
- Six.

1103
00:51:36,403 --> 00:51:37,941
Okay, I'll take it.

1104
00:51:37,942 --> 00:51:39,672
