Usually, we have it on birthdays and big parties.

1121
00:52:52,642 --> 00:52:54,812
So it's a festive dish.

1122
00:52:55,052 --> 00:52:57,681
And the sauce is very good with the rice.

1123
00:52:57,682 --> 00:52:59,582
So you can mix it and eat.

1124
00:53:00,122 --> 00:53:02,191
More rice is on the house,

1125
00:53:02,192 --> 00:53:04,421
