1132
00:53:22,712 --> 00:53:23,971
Great.

1133
00:53:23,972 --> 00:53:24,982
(Already excited)

1134
00:53:28,012 --> 00:53:29,652
I'm fully focused on eating.

1135
00:53:30,112 --> 00:53:32,122
Cool.

1136
00:53:32,922 --> 00:53:36,422
