1141
00:53:47,902 --> 00:53:50,472
(Digging in again)

1142
00:53:50,902 --> 00:53:52,572
(Impressed)

1143
00:53:53,672 --> 00:53:55,312
My goodness, it's delicious.

1144
00:53:57,112 --> 00:53:59,242
(A generous amount of sauce on the white rice)

1145
00:53:59,512 --> 00:54:01,682
(Mix the two well.)

1146
00:54:03,982 --> 00:54:07,222
