1147
00:54:07,552 --> 00:54:09,122
I like the meat the most.

1148
00:54:12,992 --> 00:54:16,592
(After that, she places meat in every spoonful.)

1149
00:54:18,302 --> 00:54:21,332
(The rice is gone in just seconds.)

1150
00:54:23,802 --> 00:54:24,841
(Eating)

1151
00:54:24,842 --> 00:54:27,242
(Finished one bowl)

1152
00:54:28,542 --> 00:54:30,111
