(it's common to wipe the remaining sauce off the plate...)

1185
00:56:13,242 --> 00:56:15,152
(with the bread if it's good.)

1186
00:56:16,652 --> 00:56:17,851
(It's the same as how Koreans mix...)

1187
00:56:17,852 --> 00:56:20,322
(the braised beef ribs sauce into rice.)

1188
00:56:23,192 --> 00:56:26,292
(Braised beef ribs, Korea's version of beef bourguignon)

1189
00:56:27,292 --> 00:56:29,962
The sauce is amazing.

1190
00:56:31,162 --> 00:56:33,762
(The sauce is all the more tasty because of its familiar taste.)

1191
00:56:38,072 --> 00:56:39,342
The sauce is incredible.

1192
00:56:41,242 --> 00:56:44,912
(Everyone is praising the braised beef ribs sauce.)

1193
00:56:47,442 --> 00:56:49,252
(Impressed)

1194
00:56:50,382 --> 00:56:51,622
It's delicious.

1195
00:56:53,582 --> 00:56:56,752
