1205
00:57:30,822 --> 00:57:32,522
This is what I recommend.

1206
00:57:32,822 --> 00:57:33,822
I see.

1207
00:57:34,022 --> 00:57:37,262
(The best method is to mix the rice into the sauce.)

1208
00:57:38,002 --> 00:57:41,372
(Mixing it with two spoons)

1209
00:57:42,632 --> 00:57:43,672
Try it.

1210
00:57:45,272 --> 00:57:47,472
(Try it, ma'am.)

1211
00:57:48,372 --> 00:57:49,442
Good.

1212
00:57:49,872 --> 00:57:52,712
(Mixing the rice in is good.)

1213
00:57:53,482 --> 00:57:55,452
(Amazed)

1214
00:57:56,682 --> 00:57:59,122
If only I could take some of the sauce home.

1215
00:58:00,622 --> 00:58:03,622
