1216
00:58:03,992 --> 00:58:08,192
(The braised beef ribs sauce captivated the French people.)

1217
00:58:09,792 --> 00:58:12,902
(The secret behind the sauce is my devotion.)

1218
00:58:13,862 --> 00:58:15,831
