1249
00:59:19,302 --> 00:59:20,732
I'll order a pan.

1250
00:59:23,072 --> 00:59:24,201
(18 euros)

1251
00:59:24,202 --> 00:59:26,142
(1 braised beef ribs)

1252
00:59:27,702 --> 00:59:30,242
New order, one person.

1253
00:59:31,642 --> 00:59:34,882
For the one person, I'll serve it on a plate, not a pan.

1254
00:59:35,282 --> 00:59:37,511
- Okay.
