1283
01:01:08,472 --> 01:01:10,142
It was good?

1284
01:01:10,342 --> 01:01:12,242
- Would you like any dessert?
- No.

1285
01:01:12,482 --> 01:01:14,281
- One for two?
- Yes.

1286
01:01:14,282 --> 01:01:15,551
