- Of course. One to share?

1289
01:01:18,622 --> 01:01:19,721
- Yes.
- Okay.

1290
01:01:19,722 --> 01:01:21,652
One to share? Perfect. Okay.

1291
01:01:22,022 --> 01:01:23,452
One to share.

1292
01:01:23,492 --> 01:01:25,291
And if it's really good, you can order another.

1293
01:01:25,292 --> 01:01:27,022
Yes, of course.

1294
01:01:27,962 --> 01:01:29,992
